'''[[dangerous]] [[goods]]'''
# Any substances, natural or man-made, which are intrinsically [[dangerous]] or otherwise pose a [[safety]] [[hazard]].  Examples are materials which are [[explosive]], [[poisonous]], [[chemical]]ly active (including [[acid]]s and other [[corrosive]]s), [[radioactive]], or [[biological]]ly active (including human [[blood]] and other medical waste).

